#

Protein Powder Waffles

25 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyeggs

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-sugar

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfastsnackeasy

Description

Fluffy and protein-packed waffles that are perfect for breakfast or a snack.

Ingredients

  • whole wheat flour: 1 cup
  • protein powder: 1/2 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • milk (or almond milk): 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • cooking spray: as needed
